HEADWORD: Oscillatory
<hw>Os"cil*la*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>oscillatoire</ets>. See <er>Oscillate</er>.]</ety> <def>Moving, or
